examples.text: We invited Mr. <w>Milroy</w> to speak at the conference next week.
Sarah <w>Milroy</w> wrote an interesting article about modern art history.

senses.sense_definition: A place name used for various towns and communities in the United States and Australia.

examples.text: The small town of <w>Milroy</w> is located in the southern part of the county.
He grew up in <w>Milroy</w> before moving to the big city for college.
